'''IEEE 802.11be''' 是計劃中 [[IEEE_802.11|802.11]] [[IEEE|IEEE]] 標準的下一次修訂。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ieee802.org/11/Reports/ehtsg_update.htm|title=IEEE P802.11 EXTREMELY HIGH THROUGHPUT Study Group|website=www.ieee802.org|access-date=2019-05-20|archive-date=2019-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190324170612/http://www.ieee802.org/11/Reports/ehtsg_update.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>預計將會被定為 '''Wi-Fi 7'''。<ref name="cnet-wifi7">{{Cite web |last=Shankland |first=Stephen |date=2019-09-03 |title=Wi-Fi 6 is barely here, but Wi-Fi 7 is already on the way - With improvements to Wi-Fi 6 and its successor, Qualcomm is working to boost speeds and overcome congestion on wireless networks. |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/wi-fi-6-is-barely-here-but-wi-fi-7-is-already-on-the-way/ |access-date=2020-08-20 |website=[[CNET|CNET]] |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916152620/https://www.cnet.com/news/wi-fi-6-is-barely-here-but-wi-fi-7-is-already-on-the-way/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ieee-wifi7">{{Cite web |last=Khorov |first=Evgeny |date=2020-05-08 |title=Current Status and Directions of IEEE 802.11be, the Future Wi-Fi 7 |url=https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9090146 |access-date=2020-08-20 |website=[[IEEE|IEEE]] |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919073727/https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9090146/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>本標準是基於 [[IEEE_802.11ax|802.11ax]] 的修訂，專注於室內外的 [[WLAN|WLAN]] 運作，面向固定的或者行人速度的設備，頻率則定在 2.4、5 或 6 GHz。<ref>{{Cite arXiv|title=IEEE 802.11be - Extremely High Throughput: The Next Generation of Wi-Fi Technology Beyond 802.11ax|last=López-Pérez|first=David|date=12 Feb 2019|class=cs.IT|eprint=1902.04320}}</ref> 
 
